long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A browser extension to see who doesn't follow you back on Instagram.

It doesn't require any use of the Instagram API, so you won't get banned for automating your account or using 3rd party apps. Everything is scraped directly from the page.
